  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Is the surgical treatment of patients with coronary heart disease using the T-graft technique
      an adequate solution that provides a sufficient myocardial flow reserve? A magnetic resonance
      examination (MRI) is required.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
